manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Find It folders put traditional folders to shame. Designed with multi-purpose to help you multi-task. Combination file folder and note pads, in white or manila, Ruled file folders, or even Calendar file folders. There’s a Find It Specialty Folder that will meet the needs of all your projects. Find It Specialty Folders Find It Folders are help you multi-task! With options like the File Folder Note Pads, Ruled File Folders, and Calendar File Folders, there is a folder for all of your filing needs. The pages of the ruled file folder and file folder Note Pads also double as an interior folder, allowing you to keep your notes and accompanying information together in the same place. With the calendar file folder, each file folder doubles as a calendar page and the interior is ruled to allow additional note taking.

File Folder Note Pad The pages of this unique writing pad also double as an interior folder, allowing you to keep your notes and accompanying information together in the same place. The 3rd-cut tabs allow you to label your files and organize them easily, so you'll always be able to find the file you need- fast. Perforated along the top so you can tear and file your notes and documents easily. Ruled File Folders Similar to the File Folder Note Pad, the Ruled File Folders let you keep your notes and materials all in one place, providing a ruled writing area right on the outside of the folder for your notes. Calendar File Folders Each file folder doubles as calendar page. Great for planning events with a specific time frame - monthly calendar page is not specifically dated, so you can use it for any month you need. And the interior is ruled to allow additional note taking.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 26, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exactly what I needed
reviews.reviewText: This is the only product I have found with vertical lines on a file folder. There are no attachments needed, it is all one item. That means there's nothing for me to lose or misplace! All of my notes can be written throughout the service and are literally part of the file. They are your standard size, so many papers fit inside. They seem pretty durable. I have been using them for about 6 months and so far they've held up well. I use erasable ink. This paper product seems to hold this ink well, it does not disappear over time... Or it hasn't yet. The only downside to these files are the price. They are quite costly. But, in the end, the price is almost a wash as I don't have to purchase other items to put inside. For me it is worth the extra money to keep everything together and important notes not at risk of being lost.They come in four different colors. I had to wait quite some time for individual packs of only the blue color. If you are a color coder, these are for you. The product is exactly as it is portrayed. The colors are bright and easy to identify. I will continue to purchase this product.
